sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant F as Flutter App
    participant S as Signaling Server

    U->>F: Nhập username / password
    F->>F: Sinh cặp khóa X25519
    F->>S: POST /api/register<br/>{username, password, publicKey}
    S->>S: bcrypt hash password<br/>lưu users.json
    S-->>F: {token, user}
    F->>F: Lưu JWT + private key<br/>(SharedPreferences)
    F-->>U: Vào màn phòng
